                        <interp inst="t18461026-name-806" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN FRESHWATER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable K</hi> 146.) I produce a certificate of Chapman's former conviction at this Court—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted the</hi> 28th <hi rend="italic">of Nov., 1842 and confined six months</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
